<L>Who cou&thorn;e ryme in englissh propurly</L>
<L N="1460">His martirdom for so&thorn;e it am not I
<PB REF="00000071.tif" N="43"></L>
<L>Ther fore I passe als lightly as I may</L>
<L>&para; It felle &thorn;at in &thorn;e seuen&thorn;e &yogh;er of may</L>
