<L N="1560">Thus ha&thorn; your ire oure lignage al fordo</L>
<L>Saf only me and wrecched Palamon</L>
<L>That Theseus martire&thorn; in prison</L>
<L>And ouer al &thorn;is to slen me vtterly</L>
<L N="1564">loue ha&thorn; his faire dart so brennyngly.</L>
<L>y-stiked &thorn;urgh my trewe carful herte</L>
<L>That schapen was my de&thorn; arst &thorn;an my scherte</L>
<L>ye sleen me with &yogh;our ey&yogh;en emelye</L>
<L N="1568">&YOGH;e ben &thorn;e cause wher fore &thorn;at I dye
<PB REF="00000074.tif" N="46"></L>
<L>Of all &thorn;e remanant / of myn o&thorn;er care</L>
