<L N="1572">And with &thorn;at word he fel doun in a traunce</L>
<L>A long tyme and aftirward he vpsterte</L>
<L>This Palamon &thorn;at &thorn;ought &thorn;at &thorn;orugh his herte</L>
<L>he felte a cold swerd sodeinliche glyde</L>
<L N="1576">ffor yre he quok no lenger wolde he byde</L>
<L>And whan &thorn;at he had herd Arcites tale</L>
