<L>ffor whom &thorn;at I haue al &thorn;is peyne and wo<MILESTONE N="23a" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L>And art my blood and to my counseil sworn</L>
<L N="1584">As I ful ofte haue told &thorn;e heer biforn</L>
