<L>ye wyse wyues &thorn;at can vnderstande</L>
<L>Thus schulde ye speke and bere hem wrong on hande</L>
<L>ffor half so boldely &thorn;er can no man</L>
<L N="228">Swere and lye as a womman can</L>
<L>I seye not &thorn;is by wyues &thorn;at ben wise /</L>
