<L>Of hire assent but herke&thorn; how I sayde /</L>
<L>Sire olde kaynard is &thorn;is &thorn;in array</L>
<L N="236">Why is my neyheboures wijf so gay</L>
<L>Sche is honoured ouer al wher sche go&thorn;</L>
<L>I sitte at hom I haue no &thorn;rifty clo&thorn;</L>
<L>What dostow at my neyhebores hous</L>
<L N="240">Is sche so fair art &thorn;ou so amerous
<PB REF="00000248.tif" N="220"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="341"></L>
<L>What roune &yogh;e wi&thorn; oure mayde benedicite</L>
<L>Sire olde lechour let &thorn;y iapes be /</L>
