<L>That I was born and make me freische and gay</L>
<L>And but &thorn;ou do to my norys honour</L>
<L N="300">And to my chambre wi&thorn;inne my bour</L>
<L>And to my fadres folk and his allyes</L>
<L>Thus seist &thorn;ou olde barel ful of lyes</L>
