<L N="304">ffor his crispe heer schynynge so gold fyn</L>
<L>And for he squyeres me bo&thorn;e vp and doun</L>
<L>yet hastow &thorn;ought and fals suspecion</L>
<L>I wil him nought &thorn;ough &thorn;ou were deed to morwe</L>
<L N="308">But telle me &thorn;is why hydest &thorn;ou with sorwe</L>
<L>Thy keyes of &thorn;i cheste away fro me /</L>
