<L N="336">haue &thorn;ou ynough &thorn;e &thorn;ar not pleyne &thorn;e</L>
<L>&thorn;ou seist also &thorn;at if &thorn;ou make vs gay</L>
<L>Wi&thorn; clo&thorn;ing or with precious array</L>
