<L>To be my warde corps as he can best</L>
<L N="360">In fei&thorn; he schal not kepe me but if me lest</L>
<L>yet cou&thorn;e I make his berd so mote I &thorn;ee</L>
<L>&thorn;ou seist eek &thorn;at &thorn;er ben &thorn;inges &thorn;ree<MILESTONE N="109a" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="marg"><I>for</I> 104</NOTE></L>
