<L>lordynges right &thorn;us &yogh;e han vnderstande</L>
<L N="380">Bar I stifly myn olde housbondes on hande</L>
<L>&thorn;at &thorn;us &thorn;ey seyden in here drunkenesse</L>
<L>And eek &thorn;at he hadde suspecion and Ielousnesse</L>
<L>On Iankyn and on my nefe also</L>
