<L N="400">ffor alle such witte is &yogh;iue vs in oure bir&thorn;e</L>
<L>Desceipte wepyng spynnyng god ha&thorn; &yogh;iue</L>
<L>To womman kyndely whil &thorn;at &thorn;ei may lyue<NOTE PLACE="marg">&para; ffallere flere nere dedit deus in muliere</NOTE></L>
<L>And &thorn;us of o &thorn;ing I auaunte me</L>
<L N="404">At &thorn;e ende I hadde &thorn;e beste in eche degre</L>
<L>By sleighte or force or by som maner &thorn;ing</L>
<L>As by continuel murmur and grucching</L>
<L>Namely a bedde hadde &thorn;ey meschaunce</L>
<L N="408">Ther wolde I chide and do hem no plesaunce</L>
