<L>Wynne who so may al are for to selle</L>
<L>Wi&thorn; empty hande men may non haukes lure</L>
<L N="416">ffor wynnyng wolde I al his lust endure</L>
<L>And make me a feyned appetyt</L>
<L>And &yogh;it in bakon hadde I neuer delit/</L>
<L>That maked me &thorn;at euer I wolde him chyde</L>
<L N="420">ffor &thorn;ough &thorn;e pope hadde sete him besyde
<PB REF="00000253.tif" N="225"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="346"></L>
<L>I wolde nou&yogh;t spare him at his oughne bord</L>
<L>ffor by my trou&thorn;e I quitte him word for word</L>
