<L>&yogh;et scholde he faile of his conclusion</L>
<L>Thenne wolde I seye now goode leef take keepe /</L>
<L N="432">how mekely loke&thorn; wilkyn oure scheepe</L>
<L>Com ner my spouse lat me ba &thorn;i cheeke</L>
<L>&yogh;e schulle be al pacient and meeke<MILESTONE N="110a" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="marg"><I>for</I> 105</NOTE></L>
