<L>This is to seye he hadde a paramour</L>
<L>And I was yong and ful of Ragerie</L>
<L N="456">Styborne and strong and ioly as a pye
<PB REF="00000254.tif" N="226"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="347"></L>
