<L N="492">Whan &thorn;at his scho ful bitterly him wrong
<PB REF="00000255.tif" N="227"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="348"></L>
<L>ffor &thorn;er was non sauf god and he &thorn;at wiste</L>
