<L N="504">God late neuer his soule come in helle /</L>
<L>And &yogh;it was he to me &thorn;e moste schrewe /</L>
<L>That feele I on my ribbes al by rewe<MILESTONE N="111a" UNIT="folio"><NOTE PLACE="marg"><I>for</I> 106</NOTE></L>
