</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>I-born he was in ferre cuntre</L>
<L>In fflaundres al be&yogh;onde &thorn;e se</L>
<L N="1910">At poperyng in &thorn;e place</L>
<L>his fader was a man ful fre</L>
<L>And lord he was of &thorn;at contre</L>
<L N="1913">As it was goddes grace</L>
</LG>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>Sire Thopas was a doughty swayn</L>
