<PB REF="00000549.tif" N="521"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="234"> apostel sai&thorn; in &thorn;e epistle [2700] &para; The ioye of god he sei&thorn; is perdurable &thorn;at is to sayn <MILESTONE N="228b" UNIT="folio">euer lastynge [2701] &para; Also trowe&thorn; and belieue&thorn; stedefastly &thorn;at he is nought wel ynorissht ne wel y-taught &thorn;at can nou&yogh;t haue pacience . . . . .<NOTE PLACE="inline">no gap</NOTE> [2702] &para; ffor salamon sai&thorn; &thorn;at &thorn;e doctrine of &thorn;e witte of man is knowen by pacience [2703] &para; And in ano&thorn;er place he sai&thorn; &para; he &thorn;at is pacient gouerne&thorn; him by gret prudence [2704] &para; And &yogh;et Salamon sai&thorn; &thorn;e angry and &thorn;e wra&thorn;ful man make&thorn; noyse &para; And &thorn;e pacient man attempereth him and stille&thorn; him. [2705] he sai&thorn; also &para; It is more wor&thorn; to be pacient &thorn;en to be right strong [2706] And he &thorn;at may haue &thorn;e lordschipe of his owne herte is more to prayse &thorn;en he &thorn;at by his force and streng&thorn;e take&thorn; grete cites [2707] &para; And &thorn;erfore sei&thorn; seint Iame in his Epistle &thorn;at pacience is a gret vertu of perfection</P>
<P>[2708] &para; Certes quod Mellibe I graunte &yogh;ou dame Prudence and pacience is a gret vertu of perfeccion [2709] &para; But euery man may not haue &thorn;e perfection &thorn;at &yogh;e sechen [2710] ne I am nought of &thorn;e nombre of right par|fyt men [2711] &para; ffor myn herte may neuer ben in pees vnto &thorn;e tyme it be venged [2712] &para; and al be it so &thorn;at it was gret peril to myn enemys to don a vilanye in takinge vengaunce vpon me [2713] &para; &yogh;et token &thorn;ey non heede of &thorn;e perille &para; But fulfilleden here wikkede wille and here corage. [2714] and &thorn;erfore me &thorn;enke&thorn; &thorn;at men ou&yogh;ten not to reproue me &thorn;ough I putte me in-to a litel peril for to auenge me [2715] &para; And &thorn;ough I do a gret excesse &thorn;at is to say &thorn;ough I do a vengance outrage by ano&thorn;er</P>
