<PB REF="00000550.tif" N="522"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="235"> outrage [2719] and &thorn;erfore &yogh;e schullen vengen &yogh;ou after &thorn;e ordre of right &thorn;at is to sayn by &thorn;e lawe and [nought] by excesse ne by outrage [2720] &para; Also if &yogh;e woln vengen &yogh;ou of &thorn;e outrage of &yogh;oure aduersaries in o&thorn;er manere &thorn;enne right comaunde&thorn;; &yogh;e synnen [2721] &para; Therfore sai&thorn; Senek &thorn;at a man schal neuer vengen schrewedenesse [by schrewedenesse] // [2722] And if &yogh;e say &thorn;at right axe&thorn; to defende violence by violence and fightynge by fyghtynge [2723] &para; Certes &yogh;e say so&thorn; when &thorn;e defens is don right anon wi&thorn;outen interualle or wi&thorn;outen taryenge or delay [2724] for to defenden him and nought for to vengen him [2725] &para; And it bihoue&thorn; &thorn;at a man putte such attemperance in his defense [2726] &thorn;at men han no cause ne matier to reproeuen him &thorn;at defende&thorn; him of excesse and of outrage . . . . .<NOTE PLACE="inline">no gap.</NOTE> [2727] &para; Par de &yogh;e knowe wel &thorn;at &yogh;e maken non deffense / as now for to defende &yogh;ou But for to venge &yogh;ou [2728] and so sewe&thorn; it &thorn;at &yogh;e haue no wille to do &yogh;oure deede attemperelly [2729] and &thorn;erfore me &thorn;enki&thorn; <MILESTONE N="229a" UNIT="folio">&thorn;at pacience is good &para; ffor Salamon sai&thorn; &thorn;at he &thorn;at is nought pacient schal haue gret harme</P>
