<P>[2877] &para; Then bygan dame prudence to make sem|blaunt of wra&thorn;&thorn;e and sayde [2878] &para; Certez sire saue &yogh;our grace &para; I loue &yogh;our honour and &yogh;our profyt as I do myn owne and euer haue doon [2879] ne &yogh;e ne noon o&thorn;er ne saugh neuer &thorn;e contrarye [2880] &para; And &yogh;et if I hadde sayd &yogh;e schulde haue purchaced &thorn;e pees and &thorn;e reconsiliacion; I nad nought mochel mystaken me ne y-sayde amys [2881] &para; ffor &thorn;e wise man saith. &thorn;e dis|sencion bygynne&thorn; by ano&thorn;er man and &thorn;e reconsilynge begynne&thorn; by &thorn;inself [2882] &para; And &thorn;e prophete sai&thorn; &para; fflee schrewednesse and do goodnesse [2883] &para; Seche pees and folwe it as mechil as in &thorn;e is / [2884] &para; &yogh;et sai&thorn; he nought &para; &yogh;et schuln &yogh;e ra&thorn;er pursewe to &yogh;our aduersaryes for pees &thorn;an &thorn;ey schuln to &yogh;ou [2885] &para; ffor I knowe wel &thorn;at &yogh;e ben so harde y-herted &thorn;at &yogh;e wolen don no &thorn;ing for me [2886] &para; And Salamon sai&thorn; &para; &thorn;at he &thorn;at ha&thorn; euer an hard herte; atte laste he schal myshappe and mystryde</P>
